{"tid":1117185,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"英國駐港澳總領事賀恩德關注修訂《逃犯條例》","createTime":"2019-04-20T13:26:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-22T16:04:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"81afb053d191328d6cba157a33d0b431e74a36d4","tid":1117185,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-20T13:26:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1453708_1_L_20190420093544.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1453708_1_L_20190420093544.jpg&h=e652784f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n英國駐港澳總領事賀恩德對於特區政府修訂《逃犯條例》表達關注，他說有很多英國人會到香港做生意、旅遊或過境，所以想清楚了解有關條文，強調並非反對修訂。<br />\n<br />\n賀恩德接受本台英文節目《The Pulse》訪問，對於香港外國記者會前副主席馬凱不獲特區政府續發工作簽證，他表示，事件令人擔心將來會否出現同類情況，尤其可能是針對英國記者。<br />\n<br />\n賀恩德形容馬凱有多年經驗，在香港亦受到一定尊重，但認為現時仍不知道事件的原因，情況令人關注。<br />\n<br />\n賀恩德又提到中國政府並不歡迎英國政府上月發表的《香港半年報告》，指自己上星期曾經到北京外交部，對方明確表明有關報告屬干預。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，尊重對方表達的意見，但指出英國作為《中英聯合聲明》的締約方，《香港半年報告》是英國總結《聲明》在香港的執行情況。"},{"pid":"d56370066e357815eab72c4bbed686f2ef437e3b","tid":1117185,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T16:01:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1453708-20190420.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1453708-20190420.htm&d=pT82QRnJ%2FvP0AhTzSnQTAkZZ0ArqIWVBMBEeODt8eII%3D&h=4757beda\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1453708-20190420.htm&h=823f12e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1453708-20190420.htm</a>"},{"pid":"409c842a5ef9e097dc5726323053b9f274ad1868","tid":1117185,"uid":60665,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T16:04:50.000Z","msg":"強調並非反對修訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}